Muchidzidzo che[[Kupimanzvimbo]], [[chiumbwa]] (Shape kuEnglish) chivakwa chinoonekwa muganhu wacho, chine mupimo unodudza kukura kwachakaita. Chiumbwa chinogona kunge chine [[nzenda]] imwe, nzenda mbiri kana nzenda nhatu. 

Muchidzidzo cheKupimanzvimbo, zviumbwa zvinosanganisira: [[mutsetse]], [[munyonya]], [[mutsendo]] iyo inokwanisa kushandiswa kutsanangudza zvimwewo zviumbwa zvemhando isiri nyore kutsangudza. Zvuimbwa zvinotaurwa zvanyanya zvinowanikwa muchinyorwa [[Kupimanzvimbo]].
